## Option 2: GitHub Pages (Good if you have a GitHub account)
1.  Go to [github.com/new](https://github.com/new) and create a repository named `tv-time-app`.
2.  **Upload Files**: Click "uploading an existing file" and drag all files from your folder to GitHub. Commit changes.
3.  **Activate Pages**:
    *   Go to **Settings** > **Pages**.
    *   Under "Source", select `main` branch and `/root` folder.
    *   Click **Save**.
4.  Your URL will be `https://<username>.github.io/tv-time-app`.

