## Option 3: Vercel (Fast & Premium)
1.  Go to [vercel.com/new](https://vercel.com/new).
2.  Import your GitHub repository (if you used Option 2) OR use the Vercel CLI.
3.  Vercel gives excellent speeds and distinct URLs (e.g., `tv-time.vercel.app`).

