## ðŸ”’ MANDATORY: Update Google Cloud Console
**The app will NOT let you log in yet.** You must tell Google that this new URL is safe.

1.  Go to the [Google Cloud Console](https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials).
2.  Select your Project ("TV Time").
3.  Click on your **OAuth 2.0 Client ID** (the one you created for this app).
4.  Look for **"Authorized JavaScript origins"**.
5.  Click **"ADD URI"** and paste your new Netlify URL (e.g., `https://rad-sunflower-12345.netlify.app`).
    *   *Note: Do not put a trailing slash `/` at the end.*
6.  Look for **"Authorized redirect URIs"**.
7.  Click **"ADD URI"** and paste the same URL.
8.  Click **SAVE**.

